# PWA Service Worker — Git + build pipeline (Stage 171.20)

## SSOT

- **Edit only** `src/pwa/sw.template.js` (placeholders: `__AIRENTO_SW_CACHE_NAME__`, `AIRENTO_PRECACHE_START` / `END`).
- **`public/sw.js` is generated** — listed in `.gitignore`. **Never commit** it.

## Build hooks (`package.json`)

| Hook | Script | Effect |
|------|--------|--------|
| `predev` / `prebuild` | `scripts/bump-sw-cache.mjs` | template → `public/sw.js`, inject `CACHE_NAME` (Vercel SHA or local id) |
| `postbuild` | `scripts/generate-sw-precache.mjs` | inject `/listings` shell `/_next/static/*` into `PRECACHE_URLS` |

Paths: `scripts/lib/sw-build-paths.mjs`.

## After clone / clean checkout

Run `npm run build` or `npm run predev` once so `public/sw.js` exists locally.

## Media delivery (catalog)

Guest catalog `sizes` / LCP priority / **PDP hero + lightbox**: **`lib/media/image-delivery.js`** + **`hooks/use-network-quality.js`**. Upload profiles stay in **`lib/services/media/media-profiles.js`**. PDP shell: **`app/listings/[id]/loading.js`**.
